    "500703": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Mavuika",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Atea",
                    "T": "When I was young, I used to sit by the hot springs and listen to the stories of warriors from all over Natlan."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Atea",
                    "T": "They attract people from all walks of life. Friends come easy here, no matter what tribe you're from."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Atea",
                    "T": "The People of the Springs have never claimed the hot springs as their own private property. They are there to bring all \"hot spring buddies\" together."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Atea",
                    "T": "It's been really nice, seeing the children of my tribe get older. It's helped me gradually understand the true value of the springs."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Atea",
                    "T": "I've witnessed their energy, their determination, their absolute passion for life..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Atea",
                    "T": "Even when they cause trouble, I never manage to hold on to my anger for long. It's unbelievable how quickly they worm their way back into my good graces."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Atea",
                    "T": "I'm certain Mualani will become a great warrior when she grows up. She possesses infinite potential... I can see it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Atea",
                    "T": "One day, when I'm no longer in fighting form, I'll come here and tell stories to all the children, just like those warriors did for me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Atea",
                    "T": "So, you better get busy, Pyro Archon, or I'll end up running out of stories, hahaha."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tenoch",
                    "T": "Our nation is engulfed in darkness, our tribes stand divided, and yet you promise victory in the distant future..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tenoch",
                    "T": "The Abyss is a cunning enemy, one that I've faced in battle many times. Were that not the case, I would never understand exercising this degree of caution."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tenoch",
                    "T": "My rage will never know absolution, and my power will no longer aid you in victory."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tenoch",
                    "T": "But, you came to me because you knew you could convince me with just a single sentence."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tenoch",
                    "T": "I understand your choice. The heroes of today will forge the path ahead with blood and fire. Just remember to earn us the victory we're owed."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tenoch",
                    "T": "Otherwise, rest assured, I'll find a way to collect the debt."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tenoch",
                    "T": "...\"For Natlan.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hine",
                    "T": "So... you're gonna head five hundred years in the future to serve as the Pyro Archon again..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hine",
                    "T": "But, what about the you from right now? You're just gonna die?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Haumia",
                    "T": "You can't ask her those questions and expect her to answer, my dear. The decision is hers to make, and she deserves our support."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Haumia",
                    "T": "We will do everything we can to rebuild the tribes. Don't you worry."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Haumia",
                    "T": "Even across time, we will all do our part to fight for Natlan's future."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hine",
                    "T": "Yeah, mom's right! We'll always believe in you, Sis!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hine",
                    "T": "Seriously, though, Dad should be here. Where is he?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Haumia",
                    "T": "I—I imagine he—he didn't know what to say, so he chose not to come at all. Don't take it to heart, my dear, that's just who he is."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Haumia",
                    "T": "Just remember — no matter what happens in the future, we will always love you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hine",
                    "T": "I'll come find you one day!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hine",
                    "T": "I know I can't live that long, but I'll think of something!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hine",
                    "T": "There has to be a way for us to meet again one day! If there's an answer out there somewhere, I'm gonna find it!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hine",
                    "T": "So, don't forget about me!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ngendi",
                    "T": "If that's your decision, then you have my full support, Archon."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kalunga",
                    "T": "May our children live to see such a lovely sun."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fietena",
                    "T": "For Natlan."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nzambe",
                    "T": "No one fights alone."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Voice of the Past",
                    "T": "The rules are my legacy. They shall grant us the strength to overcome the next tragedy."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Voice of the Past",
                    "T": "War forged the six tribes, taught us how to fight, instilled in us what it means to love..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Voice of the Past",
                    "T": "Who will be the one to bring this to an end?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mavuika",
                    "T": "We are the inheritors of memory and legend."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mavuika",
                    "T": "Those who grew alongside sun and wind."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mavuika",
                    "T": "Those who forged our own destiny and future."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mavuika",
                    "T": "That is Natlan's fire, the lifeblood of our nation."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
